title: Definitive Guide to Science Fiction Television Encyclopedia (5th
description:
Hughly Expanded 5th Edition of the Science Fiction Television Encyclopedia, updated and revised, with a lot more episode guide details, and nearly 60 new shows added since the last edition. And thousands of additions and corrections.

For the 5th edition we have covered, 1164 television shows, 908 pictures, 24,108 episode titles, and 2089 books. The main body of text is 5250 pages long. The main body of the text is just under 3 million words long.
